@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20

actor "Khách hàng" as User
participant "ProfileService (JS)" as Frontend
participant "UserController" as Controller
participant "UserServiceImpl" as Service
participant "ICustomerRepository" as CustomerRepo
participant "IMembershipTierRepository" as TierRepo

User -> Frontend: 1. Truy cập profile.html → xem phần Hạng thành viên
Frontend -> Controller: 2. GET /api/users/me
Controller -> Service: 3. getMyProfile(username)

Service -> CustomerRepo: 4. findByUsername(username)
Service -> TierRepo: 5. findTopByMinPointLessThanEqualOrderByMinPointDesc(point)
Service -> Service: 6. refreshTier() → setMembershipTier nếu có
Service -> Service: 7. Xây dựng UserProfileResponse\n(membershipTier, point, discountRate, benefits)

Service --> Controller: 8. UserProfileResponse
Controller --> Frontend: 9. 200 OK + JSON

Frontend -> Frontend: 10. renderProfile()
note right of Frontend
  - Hiển thị tierBadge
  - Hiển thị membershipPoint
  - Hiển thị membershipDiscount
    (Math.round(discountRate*100) + "%")
  - Hiển thị membershipBenefitsText
end note

== Trường hợp thanh toán thành công ==
alt Khi thanh toán thành công (từ payment-result.html)
    PaymentService -> Service: 11. Cập nhật point + refresh tier
    Service -> TierRepo: 12. findTopByMinPointLessThanEqualOrderByMinPointDesc(point mới)
    Service -> CustomerRepo: 13. save(customer)
end

User <-- Frontend: 14. Xem rõ hạng thành viên, điểm tích lũy, mức giảm giá & quyền lợi
@enduml